---
<section class="section menu" id="menu">
  <div class="inner menu-card">
    <h2 class="menu-title">鑑定料金 / メニュー</h2>
    <div class="menu-block">
      <div class="menu-groups">
        <div class="menu-group">
          <h4 class="menu-group-title">個人鑑定（対面）</h4>
          <dl class="price-list">
            <div class="price-row"><dt>30分</dt><dd>10,000円</dd></div>
            <div class="price-row"><dt>60分</dt><dd>20,000円</dd></div>
            <div class="price-row"><dt>以降15分単位</dt><dd>5,000円</dd></div>
          </dl>
        </div>
        <div class="menu-group">
          <h4 class="menu-group-title">オンライン鑑定（LINEビデオ通話）</h4>
          <dl class="price-list">
            <div class="price-row"><dt>30分</dt><dd>8,000円</dd></div>
            <div class="price-row"><dt>60分</dt><dd>16,000円</dd></div>
            <div class="price-row"><dt>90分</dt><dd>20,000円</dd></div>
          </dl>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="menu-block">
      <h3 class="menu-block-title">法人・企業鑑定</h3>
      <div class="menu-group">
        <h4 class="menu-group-title">企業鑑定（法人様向け）</h4>
        <p class="menu-desc">経営者様・企業様向けの継続サポートです。事業の流れ、人間関係、従業員様との関係性、今後の方向性など、経営に関するご相談を承っております。</p>
        <dl class="price-list">
          <div class="price-row"><dt>1ヶ月</dt><dd>100,000円（税込）</dd></div>
        </dl>
        <p class="menu-note-label">期間中は、下記すべてをご利用いただけます。</p>
        <ul class="menu-features">
          <li>対面鑑定</li>
          <li>オンライン鑑定</li>
          <li>LINE相談</li>
          <li>メール相談</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style lang="scss">
  @use "../../styles/variables" as *;
  @use "../../styles/mixins" as *;

  .menu-card {
    max-width: 820px;
    background-image: url('../../assets//images/card-bg.png');
    background-size: 100% 100%;
    background-repeat: no-repeat;
    background-position: center;
    border-radius: 30px;
    padding: clamp(56px, 9vw, 96px) clamp(40px, 8vw, 80px);

    @include sp {
      padding: 48px 28px;
    }
  }

  .menu-title {
    text-align: center;
    font-size: clamp(1.6rem, 5vw, 2rem);
    color: #5c4d2a;
  }

  .menu-block {
    margin-top: 50px;
  }

  .menu-block-title {
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 1.4rem;
    color: #5c4d2a;
    padding-bottom: 10px;
    margin-bottom: 28px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(160, 140, 80, 0.5);
  }

  .menu-groups {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 32px;

    @include tb {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 28px;
    }
  }

  .menu-group-title {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: #6b5b2e;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }

  .price-row {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: baseline;
    gap: 12px;
    padding: 8px 0;
    border-bottom: 1px dashed rgba(160, 140, 80, 0.45);

    dt {
      font-weight: normal;
    }

    dd {
      font-weight: bold;
      color: #8a6d22;
      white-space: nowrap;
    }
  }

  .price-list {
    margin-top: 20px;
  }

  .menu-note-label {
    margin-top: 20px;
    color: #6b5b2e;
  }

  .menu-features {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 10px;
    margin-top: 12px;

    li {
      padding: 4px 16px;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      background-color: rgba(231, 213, 133, 0.35);
      border: 1px solid rgba(160, 140, 80, 0.4);
      border-radius: 50px;
    }
  }
</style>